1
00:00:05,070 --> 00:00:07,570
Now, what have we learned?

2
00:00:07,620 --> 00:00:09,200
Lots of control...
Good.

3
00:00:09,240 --> 00:00:10,910
...Screaming
and hollering.

4
00:00:10,950 --> 00:00:13,210
Yes.
And most importantly...

5
00:00:13,250 --> 00:00:14,960
...Passion.
Right.

6
00:00:14,960 --> 00:00:17,670
So, now that you know
the elements of a good cheer,

7
00:00:17,710 --> 00:00:19,040
let's hear one!

8
00:00:19,090 --> 00:00:21,210
[ Inhales deeply ]
Yay.

9
00:00:21,250 --> 00:00:22,170
Ugh!

10
00:00:22,210 --> 00:00:24,550
You're gonna cheer for me
like that?

11
00:00:24,590 --> 00:00:26,260
Louder.
Yay.

12
00:00:26,300 --> 00:00:27,760
Louder!
Yay.

13
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:29,600
Louder!!

14
00:00:29,640 --> 00:00:31,680
[ Inhales deeply ]

15
00:00:31,720 --> 00:00:32,890
[ Meekly ] yay.

16
00:00:32,930 --> 00:00:34,980
Ugh!

17
00:00:34,980 --> 00:00:36,690
Too loud?

